</div>


<p>Hillel Wayne did a great talk about
<a href='https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MYucYon2-lk'>advanced testing with Hypothesis and contracts</a>,
but he also excelled in a different way:</p>

<!-- https://twitter.com/nedbat/status/994974183724666880 -->
<div class="fake-tweet-card">
