  <p class="text">Amazing. @hillelogram passes out homemade granola bars because his talk is just before lunch. #pycon2018</p>
  <div class="tweet-time">12:15 PM · May 11, 2018</div>
</div>


<p>One goof by the program committee this year: it seemed like often same-topic
talks were scheduled in the same time slot. There were four testing talks all
scheduled at the same time.  One was by Justin Crown
(<a href='https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LDdUuoI_lIg'>"WHAT IS THIS MESS?" — Writing tests for pre-existing code bases</a>),
who I met in the hallway:</p>

