<p>One of the interesting experiences at PyCon is finally meeting face-to-face
with people that you've built a strong online-only friendship with, like
<a href='https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hhj7eb6TrtI'>Mariatta Wijaya</a>.</p>

<p>It's fun to be captured by Kenneth Reitz, but maybe not outside where it's
windy?</p>

