<p>David Beazley <a href='https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zJ9z6Ge-vXs'>showed off</a>
how to use the latest meta-programming tools in Python 3.6 to implement a
parser generator:</p>

<!-- https://twitter.com/nedbat/status/995345215148916736 -->
<div class="fake-tweet-card">
