  <p class="text">I don’t know what’s more entertaining, @dabeaz’s talk, or the mystified moaning from the guy behind me :) #pycon2018</p>
  <div class="tweet-time">12:49 PM · May 12, 2018</div>
</div>


<p>Ying Li's keynote was a masterful explanation of
<a href='https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VJ0vibC_Hl0&amp;t=2107s'>web security as told through a children's book</a>.
Then Qumisha Goss (who I met at breakfast!) did a
<a href='https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VJ0vibC_Hl0&amp;t=4050s'>great keynote about teaching
urban kids programming at a public library</a>:</p>

<!-- https://twitter.com/Gre7gL/status/995301519107993605 -->
